Menu_SetClickShow
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Menu=>menu/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Menu_SetClickShow
Veneer:	<menu_set_click_show>
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = Menu object ID
r2 = 12
r3 = component id of entry
r4 = object id to show
r5 = show flags: bit 0:
       Set   - show transiently
       Unset - show persistently
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:		Method sets show event for an entry on a menu.